official_title: A resolution directing the Clerk of the House to appear in the United States District Court for the Eastern District of Wisconsin at 11 ante-meridian on September 22, and to bring certain papers in possession and under the control of the House of Representatives.

summary.text: Directs the Clerk of the House to appear in the United States District Court for the Eastern District of Wisconsin at 11 A.M. on September 22, 1975, and to bring certain papers in possession and under the control of the House of Representatives.
